comment:
* This class represents the presentation specification by which an inline suggestion
 * should abide when constructing its UI. Since suggestions are inlined in a
 * host application while provided by another source, they need to be consistent
 * with the host's look at feel to allow building smooth and integrated UIs.

variables.name: mMinSize
variables.comment: The minimal size of the suggestion.

variables.name: mMaxSize
variables.comment: The maximal size of the suggestion.

variables.name: mStyle
variables.comment:
* The extras encoding the UI style information. Defaults to {@code Bundle.Empty} in which case * the default system UI style will be used. * *

Note: There should be no remote objects in the bundle, all included remote objects will * be removed from the bundle before transmission.

methods.name: public void filterContentTypes()
methods.comment:
* Removes the remote objects from the {@code mStyle}.
     * @hide

methods.name: public Size getMinSize()
methods.comment: * The minimal size of the suggestion.

methods.name: public Size getMaxSize()
methods.comment: * The maximal size of the suggestion.

methods.name: public Bundle getStyle()
methods.comment:
* The extras encoding the UI style information. Defaults to {@code Bundle.Empty} in which case * the default system UI style will be used. * *

Note: There should be no remote objects in the bundle, all included remote objects will * be removed from the bundle before transmission.
